 Conclusions:

We described a differential expression pattern in NECD suggesting intricate interactions in gene regulation affecting skin structural integrity, cell adhesion and migration, and the HLA system. Our results shed new light for understanding the mechanisms underlying this entity: (normal’ > KRT16, KRT17), the HLA system (

